{"tid":2382672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★油麻地封區｜檢測商稱突襲碧街僅7小時預備　曾穿街坊裝勘察環境","createTime":"2021-01-27T12:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T12:08:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf47c5e9b82000b2003c2248b8331d813cacf67e","tid":2382672,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210127/431179756164091904624758.jpeg/7Mq395XgkEnlijARjETLEyaKHx2pT6CSXyakHV8mpB0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210127%2F431179756164091904624758.jpeg%2F7Mq395XgkEnlijARjETLEyaKHx2pT6CSXyakHV8mpB0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=14b6191f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n負責檢測的承辦商「相達生物科技」昨午12時收到政府通知要做「救火隊」，招彥燾指車上的工具已齊備，所以籌備時間都充裕，相信熟習流程後，預備時間可縮短至3小時。他又透露政府要求他們切勿「走漏風聲」，他昨午兩點半時曾到封區街道視察，亦要<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>穿上「街坊裝」，「無人知道我係先頭部隊嚟勘察」。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/580061/%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80-%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E5%95%86%E7%A8%B1%E7%AA%81%E8%A5%B2%E7%A2%A7%E8%A1%97%E5%83%857%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E9%A0%90%E5%82%99-%E6%9B%BE%E7%A9%BF%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E8%A3%9D%E5%8B%98%E5%AF%9F%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F580061%2F%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580-%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%2583%25857%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25A0%2590%25E5%2582%2599-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%259D%258A%25E8%25A3%259D%25E5%258B%2598%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25A2%2583&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=2d1ad1ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6